Body: www.rewards.com *Share-a-link* allows you to share a link to any store (ex.) Kohl's. The link will allow anyone who shops through your link to earn crypto for you.  How is this possible?  1. Create an account at Rewards.com.  2. Select all stores tab, click heart icon on your favorite merchants.  3. Click *Share-A-Link tab at the top of webpage.  4. Copy your custom link.  5. Send to friends, acquaintances, family, etc..   They shop at the stores through your link; all commission goes straight to your rewards wallet!  easy as that... The market it down, so say you accumulate a decent amount of Crypto by people shopping through your link, you will be sitting well off with little to no effort.
